      <item>
        <title>The capture doesn&#39;t work on Apple Watch like before</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[agiletortoise]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I’m assuming you updated to watchOS 8.</p>
<p>Apple combined dictation and scribble input in the same input dialog in watchOS 8. Most of the Summer through the beta cycle, it would remember the last one you used - but currently, it seems to always default to scribble and you have to tap to switch to dictation.</p>
<p>Quite annoying, but I can see the same behavior in any app (Messages, etc.) - at least on watchOS 8.1b2.</p>
<p>Unfortunately, not something I can override - it’s a system issue.</p>
