      <item>
        <title>The capture doesn&#39;t work on Apple Watch like before</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[sylumer]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>In the watch face, switch the complication from <em>Capture</em> to <em>Capture With Options</em>, then switch it back again.</p>
<p>I had the behaviour you describe happen once so far and figured it was a glitch, and this forced reapply worked for me in resolving it.</p>
